description:
Happy Holidays! Hogtied's little Christmas present to you is a BONUS UPDATE.
The long awaited and highly acclaimed series is back! CABO the return.
Four roommates are looking for someone to fulfill their ultimate fantasy. The girls want to find someone to capture them all and put them into bondage in a controlled and consensual environment. They are wiling to pay top dollar for their fantasy to come true. After raising their money and filling out their limit sheets, they go to the "man" to see if he will take on the job. He agrees to the girls "role play fantasy" and will make it happen sometime within the next year.
title: Cabo, the Return. Part 1
